# Database Operations Using SQLite

## Objective
This project demonstrates CRUD operations using Python and SQLite.

## Tools Used
- Python
- sqlite3 module
- DB Browser for SQLite

## Features
- Create database and tables
- Insert user records
- Fetch and display records
- Update records
- Delete records
- Parameterized queries to prevent SQL injection

## How to Run
1. Clone repository
2. Run:
   python database_app.py

## Output
SQLite database file (users.db) is generated automatically.
